            <li><strong>HEPA Filtration:</strong> Hospital-grade filtration for allergy and asthma sufferers</li>
            <li><strong>Fresh Air Ventilation:</strong> Bring in filtered outdoor air to reduce indoor pollutants</li>
          </ul>

